      "start": 99.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 110,
      "text": "🎵 In ecstasies of a lie all their hate... 🎵",
      "start": 104.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 114.44000244140625,
      "text": "🎵 And death it despises... 🎵",
      "start": 110
    },
    {
      "end": 121,
      "text": "🎵 And you... 🎵",
      "start": 114.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 128,
      "text": "🎵 And it all... 🎵",
      "start": 122.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 130.83999633789062,
      "text": "🎵 I see... 🎵",
      "start": 128.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 136.27999877929688,
      "text": "🎵 Is misery... 🎵",
      "start": 130.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 139.33999633789062,
      "text": "🎵 Yeah, misery flying inside it all... 🎵",
      "start": 136.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 142.86000061035156,
      "text": "🎵 Misery coming to take us all... 🎵",
      "start": 140
    },
    {
      "end": 145,
      "text": "🎵 Take it all... 🎵",
      "start": 142.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 149.05999755859375,
      "text": "🎵 From me before I love it too much... 🎵",
      "start": 145
    },
    {
      "end": 151.27999877929688,
      "text": "🎵 Yeah... 🎵",
      "start": 149.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 157.4199981689453,
      "text": "🎵 Take it all from me before I love it too much... 🎵",
      "start": 151.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 160,
      "text": "🎵 Cause I'll take it all... 🎵",
      "start": 157.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 162.17999267578125,
      "text": "🎵 Take it all... 🎵",
      "start": 160
    },
    {
      "end": 165.82000732421875,
      "text": "🎵 I'll take your soul... 🎵",
      "start": 162.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 171.4600067138672,
      "text": "🎵 If you let me love you just like rock and roll... 🎵",
      "start": 165.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 177.16000366210938,
      "text": "🎵 Please don't be the one to deny... 🎵",
      "start": 171.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 182.10000610351562,
      "text": "🎵 All my love, the pulse it's inside... 🎵",
      "start": 177.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 184.1999969482422,
      "text": "🎵 Goes deeper... 🎵",
      "start": 182.10000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 187.4600067138672,
      "text": "🎵 Still feeling you far away... 🎵",
      "start": 184.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 190,
      "text": "🎵 It goes deeper... 🎵",
      "start": 187.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 194.13999938964844,
      "text": "🎵 Still healing me far away... 🎵",
      "start": 190
    },
    {
      "end": 199.32000732421875,
      "text": "🎵 Beyond the times... 🎵",
      "start": 194.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 202.94000244140625,
      "text": "🎵 We've locked away... 🎵",
      "start": 199.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 205.5800018310547,
      "text": "🎵 Holiday... 🎵",
      "start": 202.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 210.0800018310547,
      "text": "🎵 Beyond your mind... 🎵",
      "start": 205.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 215.89999389648438,
      "text": "🎵 They still find a way to eat me away... 🎵",
      "start": 210.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 222.16000366210938,
      "text": "🎵 Because hope cries when the devil broke... 🎵",
      "start": 215.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 227.32000732421875,
